listing.description:
APP Kirrane Auctioneering welcomes you to your dream house in Tuam Town.  This modern, turnkey property offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience.  With three spacious bedrooms and a cozy mid-terrace layout, there's plenty of room for you and your loved ones.

One of the highlights of this home is the energy efficient electric heating system, ensuring warmth and comfort all year round.  no need to worry about chilly winters! The property offers 89.16m2 accommodation with a C2 Building Energy Rating. 

The location is truly unbeatable.  Being within walking distance of Tuam Town means you'll have easy access to a variety of shops, service providers, and leisure facilities.  Plus, with a regular bus service to Galway City, you can easily explore all that the city has to offer including; hospitals, universities, an array of employment opportunities train service, tourist attractions and historical architecture. 

Accommodation comprises of a freshly painted and decorated interior, spacious entrance hallway with carpet staircase to sleeping accommodation.  Timber flooring and energy efficient electric heater.
Sitting room is spacious and bright with timber flooring, window blinds fitted and open fire with feature fireplace.  Tastefully decorated.  
Open plan kitchen come dining room with timber floor, modern painted kitchen with fitted electric hob and oven.  Tiled splash back areas.  Rear access from the kitchen area.  
Down stairs bathroom with tiled floor and splash back area.  Fitted with white bathroom ware and electric shower.
Upstairs offers carpet staircase with timber landing.  
Three double bedrooms with varnished timber flooring.  Fitted wardrobes and window blinds.  Generously sized bedrooms, bright and nicely painted.
Large bathroom with tiled floor, white bathroom ware.  Insulated cylinder and shelved hotpress.  Attic access from landing area.  

Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this house your home or ideal investment property that would generate an 8% yield at 1300pcm rent.  The property is currently owner occupied.  Please contact the Sole Selling Agents APP Kirrane Auctioneering to arrange a viewing.  your dream home awaits.

Services: mains water, mains drainage, mains sewage, electricity, phone and broadband available.
Eircode: H54 E293.

Please Note: These particulars are for general information only for this property. The details contained are not to be relied upon as statements or representations of fact. Whilst every care is taken in the preparation of the property details, neither APP Kirrane Auctioneering or the vendor accept any liability for the details contained in the description of the property. The interested persons must satisfy themselves by viewing the property or employ somebody to inspect the property on their behalf. No Auctioneer or Staff Member employed by APP Kirrane Auctioneering in either; Main Street, Ballyhaunis, Co. Mayo or Bohermore, Galway has any authority to make or give any representation or warranty whatever in relation to this property.
